ReleaseYear: Year in which the token was released
Issuer: Name of the legal entity issuing the token
IssuerIsPubliclyTraded: True if the issuer is publicly traded
PublicTradedExchange: Name of the exchange on which the issuer is listed
PublicTradedExchangeTicker: Ticker of the issuer on the exchange on which the issuer is listed
DomiciledIn: Country or jurisdiction in which the issuer is domiciled in
IsEUDomiciled: True if the issuer is domiciled in the EU
NationalityOrCountryOfBirthOfCEO: Nationality of the CEO, Country of Birth if nationality is unknown
WhitepaperURL: URL at which the whitepaper of the issuer is available at
RegulatoryFramework: Name of the regulatory framework the issuer follows in the EU
LicenceNumber: Identifier related to the licence of a regulated actor
WeblinkToRegulatorService: URL of a service provided by a relevant regulatory authority to check the authenticity of licence information
IsEURegulated: True if the issuer is regulated under EU law
IsMiCACompliant: True if the issuer is MiCA compliant
MiCATokenType: Description of how the issuer's tokens are regulated under MiCA
